<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title> {{title}} </title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2>Welcome to Benford's Law Validation Checker!</h2>
    <p>This is a simple web application that allows you to test whether a given set of numbers satisfies Benford's Law of not with 2% margin for error.</p>
    <p>To get started, click the "Choose File" button below and select a CSV file containing a single column of numbers with at least 10,000 rows.</p>
    <form method="post" action="/checker" enctype="multipart/form-data">
      <input type="file" name="file">
      <br>
      <input type="submit" value="Submit">
    </form>
  </body>
</html>